SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 33 - The Concrete Pump Has Become
 Self-Aware
DESCRIPTION:Back to the construction site where the machinery now appears
 to have opinions of its own. We're building, troubleshooting, and possibly
 negotiating with heavy equipment. Construction Simulator is back - bigger
 and better than ever! Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them
 brand new to the franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge
 maps - on your own or with your friends!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gmd0HEz-mlk
CATEGORIES:Construction Simulator
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23482211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260512T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T205300Z
DTSTART:20260602T203000Z
DTEND:20260602T223000Z
SUMMARY:Duck Side of the Moon | Ep. 2 - Floating Through Space With
 Maximum Cuteness
DESCRIPTION:More cozy moon adventures await! Relaxed vibes, adorable
 floating ducks, and a surprisingly peaceful trip through space. Waddle and
 fly as a duck in space! Explore every corner of the galaxy and find
 curious creatures and materials along the way. Craft gadgets, upgrade your
 spaceship, and get cozy in this relaxing adventure.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k3D8Tkj6tW4
CATEGORIES:Duck Side of the Moon
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
