UID:stream-23492211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260513T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T205300Z
DTSTART:20260603T203000Z
DTEND:20260603T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite III | Ep. 2 - Gaberoun
DESCRIPTION:The desert campaign continues with stealth, precision
 shooting, and tense tactical moments where one wrong move changes
 everything. Sniper Elite 3 is a tactical third-person shooter that
 combines stealth, gameplay choice and genre-defining ballistics with huge,
 open levels and the exotic terrain of World War 2 North Africa.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nR4h99EKmzU
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite III
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23502211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260514T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T205300Z
DTSTART:20260604T203000Z
DTEND:20260604T223000Z
SUMMARY:Outbound | Ep. 2 - Powered by Tea and Solar Panels
DESCRIPTION:Back on the open road for another cozy road-trip adventure.
 Warm lights, quiet journeys, and enough tea to keep the van running...
 probably. Explore a colourful world and build your own cosy home on
 wheels. Craft workstations, and source energy from the sun, wind, or
 water. Upgrade and customize your vehicle, grow crops, and live
 sustainably off-grid with up to 4 players.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SOKlU5PA8S8
CATEGORIES:Outbound
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23512211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260515T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T205300Z
DTSTART:20260605T203000Z
DTEND:20260605T223000Z
SUMMARY:Red Dead Redemption II | Ep. 14 - Keep Riding. Don't Look Back
DESCRIPTION:The frontier journey continues with hard roads, difficult
 choices, and a world that never stops moving forward. Arthur Morgan and
 the Van der Linde Gang are outlaws on the run. With federal agents and
 bounty hunters massing on their heels, the gang must rob, steal, and fight
 their way across the rugged heartland in order to survive.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7t_hdaiBx-o
CATEGORIES:Red Dead Redemption II
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
