LAST-MODIFIED:20260608T205300Z
DTSTART:20260606T203000Z
DTEND:20260606T223000Z
SUMMARY:Fallout 4 | Ep. 49 - This Park Was Shut Down for a Reason
DESCRIPTION:Another trip into the Wasteland where \"safe\" is always
 relative. Expect danger, chaos, and the usual questionable
 decision-making. As the sole survivor of Vault 111, you enter a world
 destroyed by nuclear war. Every second is a fight for survival, and every
 choice is yours. Only you can rebuild and determine the fate of the
 Wasteland. Welcome home.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyXTmVsKhK4
CATEGORIES:Fallout 4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
