SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 34 - The Pump Can't Hurt Me
 Anymore... Right?
DESCRIPTION:Back on the construction site and ready to continue building -
 assuming the concrete pump doesn't have other plans. Surely we've won this
 battle by now... right? Construction Simulator is back - bigger and better
 than ever! Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them brand new to
 the franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge maps - on
 your own or with your friends!
